OL,3,CCCTV shows moment welder was crushed
OL,4,Cat Sunderland shipyard
OL,6,FCCTV has captured the moment a welder
OL,7,Fwas crushed while working at a
OL,8,Fshipyard, resulting in him being
OL,9,F'bedbound for a month'.
OL,11,FDavid Vinsome sustained multiple rib
OL,12,Ffractures as well as internal
OL,13,Finjuries, including an abdominal wall
OL,14,Fburst, following the incident at
OL,15,FPallion Shipyard on October 18 2022.
