OL,3,CCCTV shows moment welder was crushed
OL,4,Cat Sunderland shipyard
OL,6,FThe 37-year-old from North Shields was
OL,7,Fcrushed between an excavation bucket
OL,8,Fand a fabrication table. Following an
OL,9,Finvestigation by the Health and Safety
OL,10,FExecutive (HSE), Midland Steel Traders
OL,11,FLtd has been fined #100,000.
OL,13,FAt the time of the incident, welders
OL,14,Fhad been using an overhead gantry
OL,15,Fcrane and a fork lift truck in tandem
OL,16,Fto rotate a large excavator bucket.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
