OL,3,CCCTV shows moment welder was crushed
OL,4,Cat Sunderland shipyard
OL,6,FDavid Vinsome was crushed as he
OL,7,Fattempted to attach the chains from
OL,8,Fthe overhead crane to the bucket, and
OL,9,Fa fork lift truck started the lifting
OL,10,Foperation, unaware of his position
OL,11,Fbehind it.
OL,13,FIn a victim personal statement, the
OL,14,Ffather-of-one, recalls how he spent
OL,15,Fnine days in hospital, before
OL,16,Freturning home.
OL,18,F"When I did come home, I was in bed
OL,19,Ffor about a month before I tried to
OL,20,Fget down the stairs," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
