OL,3,CCCTV shows moment welder was crushed
OL,4,Cat Sunderland shipyard
OL,6,F"My partner is a NHS nurse, so she
OL,7,Fhelped a lot. I am still suffering a
OL,8,Flot of pain with my shoulder. I have a
OL,9,Fdaughter and I cannot do the school
OL,10,Frun anymore or take her out for meals
OL,11,For ice cream.
OL,13,F"I am worried about getting back to
OL,14,Fwork. I don't know when that will be
OL,15,For how I will manage. I don't think I
OL,16,Fwill go back to welding."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
