OL,4,Cat Sunderland shipyard
OL,6,FThe investigation by the Health and
OL,7,FSafety Executive (HSE) found Midland
OL,8,FSteel Traders Ltd had failed to ensure
OL,9,Fthat the lifting activity was properly
OL,10,Fplanned by a competent person, or
OL,11,Fcarried out in a safe manner.
OL,13,FThey also failed to produce a lifting
OL,14,Fplan, and to establish a safe system
OL,15,Fof work for this activity ` leading to
OL,16,Fa breakdown of communication between
OL,17,Fthe multiple operators involved.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
