OL,3,CCCTV shows moment welder was crushed
OL,4,Cat Sunderland shipyard
OL,6,FHSE inspector Matthew Dundas said:
OL,7,F"Lifting operations can often put
OL,8,Fpeople at great risk, as well as
OL,9,Fincurring great costs when they go
OL,10,Fwrong.
OL,12,F"It is therefore important to properly
OL,13,Fresource, plan and organise lifting
OL,14,Foperations so they are carried out in
OL,15,Fa safe manner.
OL,17,F"Had that been done in this case then
OL,18,FMr Vinsome wouldn't have been so
OL,19,Fseriously injured.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
