OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F425A1740673714
OL,3,CCCTV shows moment welder was crushed
OL,4,Cat Sunderland shipyard
OL,6,F"HSE provides detailed guidance on
OL,7,Flifting operations including the
OL,8,Fimportance on how they should be
OL,9,Fproperly resourced, planned and
OL,10,Forganised, to enable them to be
OL,11,Fcarried out in a safe manner."
OL,13,FMidland Steel Traders Ltd, Portobello
OL,14,FInd Est, Shadon Way, Chester le
OL,15,FStreet, pleaded guilty to breaching
OL,16,Fthe Sections 2(1) and 3(1) of the
OL,17,FHealth and Safety at Work etc. Act
OL,18,F1974. The company was fined #100,000
OL,19,Fand told to pay #4,916 costs at
OL,20,FNewcastle Magistrates' Court on
OL,21,FFebruary 13 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
